   7:matacc.c      **** /*************************************************
   8:matacc.c      **** * Name:        matacc
   9:matacc.c      **** *
  10:matacc.c      **** * Description: Multiplies a row of A or A^T, generated on-the-fly,
  11:matacc.c      **** *              with a vector of polynomials and accumulates into the result.
  12:matacc.c      **** *
  13:matacc.c      **** * Arguments:   - poly *r:                    pointer to output polynomial to accumulate in
  14:matacc.c      **** *              - polyvec *b:                 pointer to input vector of polynomials to multiply wit
  15:matacc.c      **** *              - unsigned char i:            byte to indicate the index < KYBER_K of the row of A o
  16:matacc.c      **** *              - const unsigned char *seed:  pointer to the public seed used to generate A
  17:matacc.c      **** *              - int transposed:             boolean indicatin whether A or A^T is generated
  18:matacc.c      **** **************************************************/
